==English==
===Phrase===
# {{surfing}} Said of challenging [[surfing]] conditions or a challenging [[wave]], and meaning that highly-[[respected]] [[waterman]] [[w:Eddie Aikau|Eddie Aikau]] (1946-1978) would take it on (go out in such conditions or [[surf]] such a wave).  Used as an [[encouragement]] for one to do the same, or as a general comment on [[difficulty]] or [[danger]].
#: 2002: ''Eddie Would Go: The story of Eddie Aikau, Hawaiian Hero'' &mdash; title of book by Stuart Coleman (ISBN 097062137X)